<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Key Takeaways</h2>



<ul>
<li>Ethereum hardware wallets offer the highest level of security for storing Ethereum offline.</li>



<li>Hardware wallets provide an extra layer of protection for assets like Ether and ERC-20 tokens.</li>



